txt.en: Spider cocoons can be found at Writhenset in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should destroy spider cocoons at Writhenset.
Spider cocoons found at Writhenset should be destroyed in order to weaken the brood of spiders lurking beneath the Wildwood.
Spiders lurk within the mines of Writhenset, beneath the Wildwood. Destroying their vile cocoons should weaken the brood and assist with making the mines safe for the Free Peoples.
